Russia will impose retaliatory sanctions on
Western nations on the basis of reciprocity, the Kremlin said on Friday. Kremlin
spokesman Dmitry Peskov said sanctions would cause problems for Russia but they
would be solvable, as it had reduced its dependence on foreign imports. Russia will impose retaliatory sanctions on
